  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not-- don't-- look away when he's coming on Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Don't make any problems.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very limited amounts, very limited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was really miserable, miserable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But whatever we had, whatever I had, I was trying to-- to get out, and my father was going-- tried-- tried very hard to get out Shabbat from work.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was extremely hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was extremely hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a-- at that time, I was a teenager.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A teenager wants-- wants to have fun, wants to have friends, go out with friends, spend time with-- with equals.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No such thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no such thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody was striving just to have enough food and to-- to save-- to save their lives as-- as much as they could because at that time already, in 1940-- late 1941, people were taken out of ghetto, hundreds of people, to be transported to extermination camps in Belzec, in Treblinka, and in Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we knew that the people were taken out of the ghetto and transported somewhere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know where yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did not have the information.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have the terrible news that the people were transported to be killed and-- and-- and burned.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know it, because the Germans were very adept at hiding, at-- at secrecy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were very adept at it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because if somebody would get-- would get wind of it, what-- what happened to these people, they would have a rebellion on their hands, like they had in-- in-- in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Warsaw Rebellion was also a-- a-- in 1943, was a result of people getting wind of what-- what was going on, what-- what-- where-- where-- where the transports were taken.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
